  "text": [
    "1",
    "God twirled",
    "across the face of",
    "what cannot be named",
    "since it was not moving.",
    "God was momentum then,",
    "that impatience",
    "with interruption,",
    "stamping time's blanks",
    "with its own image.",
    "2",
    "Now her theme will be",
    "that she has escaped",
    "certain destruction,",
    "that she is",
    "impossibly lucky.",
    "This theme should be jaunty",
    "but slightly discordant,",
    "coming in, as it does,",
    "so late.",
    "The character",
    "associated with this theme",
    "should be dressed",
    "in markedly old-fashioned clothing\u2014",
    "a hoop skirt perhaps\u2014",
    "while everyone else",
    "is in cut-offs,",
    "ready for the barbeque."
  ],
  "title": "Hoop",
  "year": ""
